title: In Your Arms By Becky Andrews EPUB EN
description:
Samantha Baker has a crush on one of the most popular 
boys in school, Phillip Corinodi. Unfortunately, he also 
happens to be going out with Tracy, the girl every guy 
wants to be with. Pretty, popular, and bitchy, she is 
everything Samantha is not. When the two spend an hour 
together in detention, Phillip strikes up a conversation 
with Samantha. They were friends once before, many years 
ago, before Phillip got popular and ditched her. Why is he 
suddenly talking to her again now, after so many years? As 
her relationship with Phillip starts to take an exciting 
new turn, she witnesses a school shooting and her life is 
threatened. Can she trust Phillip enough to tell him the 
truth before she becomes the next target?



In Your Arms
By Becky Andrews
